name: P&P Dreamy Gradients - CS
description:
Enhance every photo with these fine, dreamy finishes.  Each gradient is a unique, artistic action.  These lovely gradients will integrate best with your photo if you use the layer mask and paint over parts of the photo you do not want to be as dreamy (such as a person or object the photo is centered around).  This set contains the following gradients in the form of actions:

Ballet Slippers
Cotton Candy
Peach Créme
Lace
Marshmallow Fluff
Blush
Petal
Powder Blue
Buttercream
Meadow
Misty Morning

(Actions are immediately downloadable upon purchase!)
